title: Camco RV Bathroom Toilet Tissue | Sewer-Safe, Septic-Safe, and Biodegradable | Designed for Trailer, Motor Home & Marine Sanitation Systems | 1-Ply Bath Tissue | 4 Rolls - 280 Sheets per Roll (40275)
description: The Camco TST 1-Ply RV and Marine Toilet Tissue is designed and approved for use in RV and marine sanitation systems. This toilet tissue provides a comfortable, dependable clean. It is flushable, clog defiant, fast dissolving, biodegradable and septic tank safe. Contains no dyes or perfumes. Contains (4) rolls with 280 sheets per roll.
